00:25:35,060 --> 00:25:36,900
 throughout the many centuries, right?

530
00:25:36,900 --> 00:25:39,380
 Yet, it stands solid as a rock

531
00:25:39,380 --> 00:25:41,220
 because who is our cornerstone?

532
00:25:41,220 --> 00:25:42,280
 Jesus Christ.

533
00:25:43,120 --> 00:25:46,520
 Therefore, we continue to be confident

534
00:25:46,520 --> 00:25:48,080
 to place ourselves as rocks

535
00:25:48,080 --> 00:25:50,920
 to continue to build this household, this church.

536
00:25:50,920 --> 00:25:55,400
 In conclusion, let me get back to my story

537
00:25:55,400 --> 00:25:58,840
 of my family few.

538
00:25:58,840 --> 00:26:01,460
 My uncles, they're currently still enemies.

