00:26:04,400 --> 00:26:07,400
 but from the way I see it,

541
00:26:07,400 --> 00:26:08,920
 there's a sense of hopelessness in them.

542
00:26:08,920 --> 00:26:10,400
 They don't know, they can't see the light

